{"tid":1097519,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊稱李家超聽到選委意見　重申逃犯條例難免追溯期","createTime":"2019-04-08T12:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T00:09:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d34e34393fc3458ab092669094cc23c5d423c5","tid":1097519,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1451825-20190408.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1451825-20190408.htm&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp1MsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=9103c0f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1451825-20190408.htm&h=e1170908\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1451825-20190408.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n全體法律界選委發表聯署聲明，促請政府撤回逃犯條例修訂草案。律政司司長鄭若驊回應表示，相信保安局局長李家超會聽到相關意見，作出適當考慮。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊強調，香港是法治社會，要有制度性方法處理處理逃犯移交，以將逃犯送回相關地方進行審訊。<br />\n<br />\n被問到法律界選委認為，政府明顯有其他合適方法處理台灣殺人案，鄭若驊表示，從法治角度需要有一個制度處理，而非每宗案件立例處理。<br />\n<br />\n至於逃犯移交是否可以就追溯期劃線或不設追溯期，她就說，逃犯條例是要處理有關疑犯所犯的罪行，因此難以免卻有關安排。"},{"pid":"c2359ca7a236c2f31bebee03a1b95359c6a71f18","tid":1097519,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"點解保安局長好似仲大權過特首同彿政司長，逃犯條例單嘢佢話晒事噉"},{"pid":"9aa754704b98fe0b8a784d26e4671551db5f8f7d","tid":1097519,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a73c00c3434fd84da8077d0d606ed9ef5db07c","tid":1097519,"uid":103981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"嘩我仲以為而家特區無律政司司長，呀鄭司長終於上番水？"},{"pid":"794655aa8793c324664c6eaa33115d4da8fa6958","tid":1097519,"uid":179409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:12:33.000Z","msg":"無追溯期點劏你班港商呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" 